headline: Fifth Third Wealth Advisors® Surpasses $3 Billion in Net New Assets Under Management, Expands Platform Capabilities
summary: CINCINNATI, July 01, 2025--Fifth Third Wealth Advisors®, a multi-custodial registered investment advisory firm, announced it has surpassed $3 billion in net new assets under management, as of June 30, marking another major milestone in the firm’s growth.
